snippet.title: PROJECT STARLINE | Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Currently in pre-production at Deadpixel Arts, Project Starline, is a sci-fi multiplayer racing game with abilities set in the 24th century where a sport called Rigout is at its highest point, being the most popular sport in the known universe.

Visit the official pages for 
Project Starline - https://projectstarline.com/
DeadPixel Arts - https://www.deadpixelarts.com

Follow DeadPixel Arts on social media:
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/deadpixelarts
Twitter - https://twitter.com/DeadPixel_Arts
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/deadpixel.arts
